src:
Former Wassup member Nari shares teaser images for her first digital single
06 Nov 2019, 18:56 by sl278



Former Wassup member Nari has released the first round of teaser images for her first digital single!
Although the name of the single has yet to be revealed, Nari stuns in red-lit images showing off her visuals and moody aura. 
She recently wrote a handwritten letter to fans about her solo release.



Check out the rest of the images below!
